{"tid":2062791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国公路大爆炸  車輛炸飛4樓高 現場磨菇雲 多人死傷","createTime":"2020-06-13T11:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T04:34:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":248,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"96572dce9294b2f1fbe9d98601d567bdc57b9977","tid":2062791,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:38:08.000Z","msg":"今（13）日下午，中國浙江台州溫嶺大溪高速公路口附近疑似一油罐車發生爆炸，巨響後現場冒出濃濃黑煙，沒多久就發現一輛疑似轎車的物體從爆炸中心彈了出來，甚至還炸飛約4層樓高。據了解，爆炸波及周邊房屋及車輛，有人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，這起事件發生在今日下午，當時這輛油罐車在高速公路口發生爆炸，震波不但把附近住家的窗戶都震碎，甚至還有一輛轎車從爆炸中心被彈出，有人就指出車頭和車身已經整個解體了。周圍一片狼藉，據了解現場有多人傷亡，目前相關救援人員也抵達現場，附近多處高速公路閘道也關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=761229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D761229&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=4e1f2a3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D761229&h=d54c4c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=761229</a>"},{"pid":"f7753bdc51918d3d653e3e45d6dc369477266d07","tid":2062791,"uid":77717,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"多難興邦，又可以刷GDP，死啲低端人口，提升人均gdp <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaa6fc059923c9bbcb10420b9dd1e299f5be241","tid":2062791,"uid":46910,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"冇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4515dc0db0b20d8baf28f4cddf1f3184a956f2b2","tid":2062791,"uid":140335,"like":93,"dislike":2,"score":91,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"爆戈下 爆到卡通笑片咁<br />\nboom~之後成塊飛左上天<br />\n支国人條命就係咁搞笑"},{"pid":"f9ae0a805044784dda4a33e65950e4e50a4d1d23","tid":2062791,"uid":310637,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:54:06